    slug: "botox-men-dating-over-40",
    title: "Botox for Men Getting Back Into Dating After 40",
    metaTitle: "Botox for Men Dating Over 40 — Looking Your Best Guide",
    description: "Re-entering the dating market after 40 — whether after divorce, the end of a long relationship, or simply not having dated for years — is a real, specific situation. Here's how Botox fits into it.",
